      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CASH CARRIAGE (5) ran right away with it after leading them home to make it two on the bounce at this track over 400m (22.97). Speedy beginner who can find the front with a clean break from the middle of the draw. Well placed and can measure up. PHOTO CRUSHER (7) is rarely far away but tends to find one better, placing six from 11 starts. Has hit the frame the last two runs, the latest when second (20.22) at Angle Park. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Must be included in calculations. FABLE LEGEND (2) ran below best last time finishing fourth (20.52) over 342m at Angle Park from Box 1. Good beginner aided by a nice draw. A big run wouldn't surprise. ROCK ON BUB (4) will give backers a sight.",
